Cybersecurity Tools;

Log - is a record of events that occur within an organization's systems.

SIEM Tools (Security Information and Event Management tool) - An Application that collects and analyzes log data to monitor critical activities in an organization

Splunk & Google chronicles

Playbook - Manual that provides details about any operational action
-- How to response and handle security breaches.

Network Protocol Analyzer (Packet Sniffer) - A tool designed to capture and analyze data traffic within a network.




